Summary: this is 2 of 4 pictures from www.sabagocam.com it's moving.cam is down
divs: Sighting Details I had this webcam as a favorite (I'm from NH and miss the seasons). I caught these pics (1 and 2 of 4 ) while just checking out the cam. I thought it was just a bird flying by but thought it looked a little like a flying saucer so I hit the screen capture button. I was surprised when the webcam refreshed 30 seconds later. Same shape but appearing to be further away. It seems to be going in a straight line. I tryed just now to get on the cam and it appears to be down right now. Google search mentions it many times.
